                <MadCap:snippetText src="../UIElements/SelectViewRibbon.flsnp" />In the <span class="Emphasis">Resources</span> section select <span class="Emphasis">SharePoint Explorer</span>. The SharePoint Explorer opens.</li>
            <li>
                <p>Locate the file(s) that you want to check out. You can use the "multi-view" to do this.</p>
                <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../UIElements/MultiViewTable.flsnp" />
